Package: scenesetr
Type: Package
Title: Construct and Render Interactive 3-Dimensional Scenes
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-11-22
Description: Construct 3-dimensional scenes with elements of three types: light, camera and scene object. Render scenes from the perspective of a camera with real-time key inputs. Add custom element behaviours to define location, rotation and colour in response to key inputs and other elements.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.11),
    methods
LinkingTo: Rcpp
